                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17971206-50-off269 t17971206-50-cd270"></join>, a feather bolster, value 3s. a feather pillow, value 2s. fifty pounds of feathers, value 30s. two linen sheets, value 4s. 6d. a woollen blanket, value 3s. three prints, framed, value 3s. a copper saucepan, value 3s. 6d. a pair of bellows, value 2s. a copper tea-kettle, value 2s. a brass stew-pan, value 12d. an iron trivet, value 6d. a flat iron, value 6d. part of a pewter dish, value Id. a pail, with an iron hoop, value 6d. a looking-glass, value 12d. and an iron key, value 3d. the property of 
